---
const painPoints = [
  "You've tried to just 'push through' but nothing changes",
  "You feel like you're constantly masking or performing for everyone around you",
  "Small tasks feel impossibly overwhelming and you can't explain why",
  "You know something isn't right but you're not sure where to start",
];
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-[var(--color-bg-alt)]">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-12">You might recognise some of this...</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      {painPoints.map((point) => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text)] font-medium leading-relaxed text-lg">{point}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-[var(--color-text-light)] mt-10 text-lg">
      If any of that sounds familiar, you're not broken. You might just need the right support.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
